g.text: Calculate total block size (header + footer + alignment + padding)
Size fits thread cache AND cache available?
Check if block can be split (size > required + MIN_SPLIT_SIZE)
Split block: create new remainder block with header/footer
Return pointer to user payload (after header)
Fallback: Request memory from OS (via mmap/sbrk)
Setup new chunk: initialize header/footer, mark as allocated
Search segregated free list by size class
Add remainder to appropriate free list
